dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Dealing with the sheer difficulty of this New Horizon course is a common theme in these Murray Cup qualifiers.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: For those of you watching who are interested in getting involved with Murray Cup racing, it really comes down to two things, practice, and a ton of credits to buy a ship.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Dealing with stress and fatigue may almost be as important in a race like this as is the ship you fly.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Little known fact, this raceway was designed from the ground up to make these pilots gently weep to themselves as they fly.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: This course is not one you want to fight against. The best bet is to close your eyes and just go along for the ride.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: It's hard to imagine what those original Murray Cup racers, using planets to mark the course, would think of today's track innovations.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: It really is austounding how there seems to be no one way to win this race. Having the fastest ship means nothing if you're going to get your ass blown off.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: One of the great things about Murray racing is how the debate over speed vs. agility vs. firepower vs defense still rages to this day.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: I'm reminded of a similar race in 2938 where all the ships also went around a track very fast.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: New Horizon, a recent edition to the Cup, has been devisive amongst pilots as they strive to master all its nuances.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Hard to believe that there was a time when the Murray Cup was just a cup owned by a guy named Murray.
